<subSubSection id="71D06508FF97FFAAFD5CB0D805A7828B" pageId="2" pageNumber="195" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="39753683FF97FFAAFD5CB0D805A7828B" blockId="2.[709,1306,2805,3230]" pageId="2" pageNumber="195">
The distributions of the subspecies are not well established. The distribution of Colombian shrew-opossums (this species and 
<taxonomicName id="FECA4D00FF97FFAAFC90B75E05CF825B" box="[778,954,3121,3150]" class="Mammalia" family="Caenolestidae" genus="Caenolestes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Paucituberculata" pageId="2" pageNumber="195" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="fuliginosus">C. fuliginosus</taxonomicName>
) are in need of focused sampling and systematic revision. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="71D06508FF97FFAAFFFEB7C800548F4A" pageId="2" pageNumber="195" type="synonymic_list">
<caption id="6DB5660BFF97FFAAFFFEB7C800548F4A" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6588411" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6588411" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6588411/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="195" targetBox="[95,686,2812,3224]" targetPageId="2">
